OOC: Are there any bots in France still if not void this.  If there are who 
are they.

::SkarBlaise::
    He headed west through what would become Germany only to arrive at what 
would become France where he saw some bots.  Thinking this would be fun he 
transforms and aims his rocket launcher at one of the bots and his laser 
canon at another.  "Do not move I will shoot.  Actually I will shoot anyway," 
he said with a sneer.
